  "description": "A photograph of Marty and his siblings. As Marty's interference threatens his parents' meeting, the siblings begin to fade from the image. The photo serves as a visual countdown: when it goes blank, Marty will cease to exist. After George and Lorraine kiss at the dance, the photo is restored.",
